<h2 id="imageTitle">
  Financial District</h2>
<h3 class="description">
  I don't really have a witty comment for this.</h3>
<h3 class="description">
  This is actually my second attempt at taking this photo. The first time it was so windy I had to hold my tripod down even with my bag weighing it down it would have been blown over. In that photo there's no reflection on the water cuz there's a bunch of big waves instead.</h3>
<h3 class="description">
  Personally it kind of bothers me because this image isn't super sharp, and I think it's actually a limitation of my lens, but ultimately it still looks pretty cool and that's what matters!</h3>
<h3 class="imageInfo">
  July 27, 2016 at Brooklyn Bridge Park - Pier 6 in Brooklyn, NY</h3>